selama 30 menit.

71
00:03:43,521 --> 00:03:45,231
Ini caramu membayar utang kepadaku.

72
00:03:45,315 --> 00:03:46,441
Jangan tanya apa-apa.

73
00:03:46,524 --> 00:03:47,650
Tentu.

74
