di legasi Amerika setelah dia sadar.

162
00:10:16,163 --> 00:10:17,582
Dia akan segera keluar.

163
00:10:18,124 --> 00:10:21,335
Setelah dia keluar,
bawa dia di tempat paling aman.

164
00:10:22,211 --> 00:10:23,421
Di mana?

165
00:10:24,088 --> 00:10:25,881
Sel penjara di Biro Kepolisian Joseon.

166
00:10:28,050 --> 00:10:28,884
Ya, Tuan.

167
00:10:34,307 --> 00:10:35,141
Aku penasaran.

168
00:10:36,142 --> 00:10:38,978
Kenapa surat itu diambil?

169
00:10:39,061 --> 00:10:40,980
Aku bahkan belum selesai membacanya.

170
00:10:54,952 --> 00:10:56,787
<i>Hidupku juga penuh warna.</i>

171
00:11:01,042 --> 00:11:02,168
<i>Bedanya,</i>

172
00:11:04,503 --> 00:11:05,671
<i> aku ingin menjadi api.</i>

173
00:12:46,313 --> 00:12:49,650
<font color="#00ffff">LEGASI AMERIKA SERIKAT
EUGENE CHOI</font>

174
00:12:55,281 --> 00:12:56,407
<i>Tuan Lee Wan-ik?</i>

175
00:12:56,490 --> 00:12:59,452
