968
01:10:09,501 --> 01:10:11,378
<i>hingga butuh satu bulan untuk diarungi.</i>

969
01:10:12,504 --> 01:10:14,172
<i>Lautan luar biasa</i>

970
01:10:14,715 --> 01:10:17,300
<i>yang berlanjut di balik cakrawala.</i>

971
01:10:19,553 --> 01:10:23,015
